{"tid":1254331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾國斌：如獨立調查涵蓋示威者組織資源可考慮 只查警方就不支持","createTime":"2019-06-24T05:27:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T05:33:52.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1db3fb6fee9b856d4df8fd735257bf08de942659","tid":1254331,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T05:27:57.000Z","msg":"逃犯條例爭議持續，政府早前宣布暫緩修例，但拒絕撤回，曾多次表明對修例有疑慮的自由黨魁鍾國斌今日表示，建議政府撤回修例，「現實情況，『暫緩』和『撤回』根本是一模一樣的事，爲何不可以講？」他認為政府宣布撤回，可以令示威者無藉口再衝擊政府。<br />\n<br />\n鍾國斌表示，明白政府有需要照顧部份支持者的感受，未必適當公開表達撤回，但既然事實上撤回和暫緩亦無分別，政府應該要考慮，如果林鄭月娥不方便親口宣布，也可以找政務司長張建宗代為處理。<br />\n<br />\n對於示威者要求設獨立調查委員會，鍾國斌表示，若委員會是針對調查警方，他不會支持，但若調查範圍廣泛，例如背後的組織策劃、示威物資資源等，則可以考慮。<br />\n<br />\n而民建聯主席李慧琼星期日出席電視節目時亦表示，特區政府宣布暫緩修例，對反送中示威的回應不實際、不對焦，若政府選擇撤回，相信民建聯支持者會理解。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E9%BB%A8%E9%8D%BE%E5%9C%8B%E6%96%8C%E5%80%A1%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%92%A4%E5%9B%9E%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82-%E6%9A%AB%E7%B7%A9%E5%92%8C%E6%92%A4%E5%9B%9E%E6%A0%B9%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%A8%A1%E4%B8%80%E6%A8%A3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD-%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E9%258D%25BE%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2596%258C%25E5%2580%25A1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%2592%25A4%25E5%259B%259E%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E8%25A8%2582-%25E6%259A%25AB%25E7%25B7%25A9%25E5%2592%258C%25E6%2592%25A4%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%25A0%25B9%25E6%259C%25AC%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25A8%25A3%2F&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVGsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=6a03c972\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD-%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E9%258D%25BE%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2596%258C%25E5%2580%25A1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%2592%25A4%25E5%259B%259E%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E8%25A8%2582-%25E6%259A%25AB%25E7%25B7%25A9%25E5%2592%258C%25E6%2592%25A4%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%25A0%25B9%25E6%259C%25AC%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25A8%25A3%2F&h=996e73de\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E9%BB%A8%E9%8D%BE%E5%9C%8B%E6%96%8C%E5%80%A1%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%92%A4%E5%9B%9E%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82-%E6%9A%AB%E7%B7%A9%E5%92%8C%E6%92%A4%E5%9B%9E%E6%A0%B9%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%A8%A1%E4%B8%80%E6%A8%A3/</a>"},{"pid":"0ea0e63d8af2ec5fadbdfe63347e7e345148c34e","tid":1254331,"uid":99018,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T05:29:21.000Z","msg":"我地有組織咩"},{"pid":"af50091a309c1f7652bb9c60c093ddccce378fcd","tid":1254331,"uid":202730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T05:29:21.000Z","msg":"背後的組織策劃 =lihkg <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n示威物資資源=Hong Kong"},{"pid":"ac8b75ae1e478295e371dc24c140d2d9a486d26f","tid":1254331,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T05:29:33.000Z","msg":"1. 有巴打昨日講，<br />\n小心會演變成獨立委員會查示威者<br />\n警監會查警察<br />\n<br />\n2. 獨立委員會既功能應該係查政府機構行為，而唔係市民？？？"},{"pid":"18d17845362d250dfa88fac129b80c645b53bea2","tid":1254331,"uid":160051,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T05:30:14.000Z","msg":"支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但查唔到有示威者資源係外國勢力提供嘅證據，啲廢老同廢中唔知會點屈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62d058ed6b60e89a3a654508a302bb97276d8a39","tid":1254331,"uid":42090,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T05:30:36.000Z","msg":"要唔要查埋共產黨比左幾多指令香港政府？"},{"pid":"f917c447e43e63b57cf3228241e25343c6c3ec78","tid":1254331,"uid":103325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T05:33:00.000Z","msg":"示威者係俾一個英國人煽動出嚟架<br />\n咪就係拎住英國護照嘅林鄭月娥囉"},{"pid":"61ea40a14a2fb2433157000e00ed54480fcbbace","tid":1254331,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco